tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_analysis (
    website_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_views INT,
    conversion_rate FLOAT,
    traffic_source VARCHAR,
    date_visited DATE
)

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    visitor_id INT,
    entry_time TIMESTAMP,
    exit_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rate (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    conversion_count INT,
    total_visits INT,
    conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name TEXT,
    target_audience TEXT,
    conversion_goal INT,
    budget DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_visited TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates (
  conversion_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_visited TEXT,
  conversion_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
  strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_name TEXT,
  description TEXT,
  start_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_id INT,
  conversion_id INT,
  conversion_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE visitors (visitor_id INT, visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP, page_visited VARCHAR(255), conversion BOOLEAN) CREATE TABLE pages (page_id INT, page_name VARCHAR(255), unique_visitors INT, total_visits INT) CREATE TABLE traffic_sources (source_id INT, source_name VARCHAR(255), visitors_from_source INT) CREATE TABLE conversions (conversion_id INT, visitor_id INT, conversion_timestamp TIMESTAMP) CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (strategy_id INT, strategy_name VARCHAR(255), target_audience VARCHAR(255), conversion_rate DECIMAL)
